\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\sl276\slmult1\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f40\lang1033\langfe2052\langnp1033\insrsid7108781 
This command guide is designed to allow modders to better understand the new aiscript commands created by Neiv and iquare.}{\f40\lang1033\langfe2052\langnp1033\insrsid10976062 
\par 
\par }{\f40\lang1033\langfe2052\langnp1033\insrsid7108781 
Many of these commands are staples of high-end AI in the modern era. It is my hope that by writing this guide and shedding more light on the use cases of these new commands, more modders will pay closer heed to the designs of their AI and find more ways t
o make compelling missions in SCBW. If you have any questions, feel free to contact me.}{\f40\lang1033\langfe2052\langnp1033\insrsid10976062 
