\par }{\f40\lang1033\langfe2052\langnp1033\insrsid7108781 `priority` specifies the priority. Higher priority is more important. Does not compete with stock AI commands such as `build` and `train`.}{\f40\lang1033\langfe2052\langnp1033\insrsid10976062 
